City of Pensacola, Florida
LIEN FOR IMPROVEMENTS
The CITY OF PENSACOLA, a Florida municipal corporation, acting pursuant to Sections 13-1-6 and 13-
1-7 Code of the City of Pensacola, does hereby claim and impose a Lien of the following described real
property located in Pensacola, Escambia County, Florida, to-wit:
FRAZIER, TIM
511 ND STREET
LT 24 AND N 1/2 OF LT 25 PEBLEYS S/D BLK 38 WEST
KING TRACT
Parcel Identification Number 000S009060024038
Real Estate Account Number 150485000
in the total amount of $219.00(Two Hundred Nineteen & 00/100)
for all cost incurred in clearing weeds, undergrowth, trash, filth, garbage or other refuse from the
aforementioned property on or about the 14th day of March 2022. Said lien shall be equal in dignity to all
other special assessments for benefits against property within the City.
DATED this 26th day of May, 2022
THE CITY OF PENSACOLA
a municipal corporation
BY:
KERRITH FIDDLER
CITY ADMINISTRATOR
& Burnett
CITY CLERK
(SEAL)
STATE OF FLORIDA
COUNTY OF ESCAMBIA
THE FOREGOING INSTRUMENT was acknowledged before me this 2 7
_ day of
May
, 2022 by Kerrith Fiddler, City Administrator of the City of Pensacola, a Florida municipal
corporation, on behalf of said municipal corporation who is personally known to me.
onecie Aufs
NOTARY PUBLIC
DONECIA GRIFFIN
Notary Public
State of Florida
Comm# HH099471
Expires 3/6/2025
Revised 1/24/2018
